a is facing a shortage<br>of vaccines for the disease and lacks health prof=
essionals with<br>knowledge of treating the disease.=0D<br>=0D<br>Diphtheri=
a is a bacterial infection that attacks the respiratory<br>tract. Airborne =
droplets transmit it and can be fatal, especially for<br>small children. If=
 an antitoxin is not administered quickly, the<br>fast-growing pseudo membr=
