 to breathe. It can be<br>life-threatening.=0D<br>=0D<br>The lack of resour=
ces to tackle the disease is a big challenge that<br>must be addressed imme=
diately to avoid a health crisis in the West<br>African country.=0D<br>=0D<=
br>"We lack health professionals who know how to recognise and treat this<b=
